channel.title: Others cant login to my server, but I can...Any help?
channel.description:
Im talking to one of my friends over IM, and hes been testing my server, and Ive been running runserver over and over,
"Starting Seekscape Server on 0.0.0.0:43594"
So, at least no errors...I logged in earlier...But my friend cannot log in with no-ip, the servers IP...anything...
Any help?...
BTW: Please dont ask if Im giving him the IP 0.0.0.0 or any of that...Of course not. Im giving him my external IP (server IP)
